@node History "Index View History"

  @{b}@{u}History@{uu}@{ub}

      Version 1.0 (21.06.96) - Initial release.

      Version 1.1 (15.08.96)
        - Index View, Integrate and Fix Index buffer I/O operations.  This
          makes Index View about 1.5 times faster.  Integrate and FixIndex
          is about 2-3 times faster now.
        - Fixed problems with "long" version of the INDEX file.  Now you
          can use Index View with info/index/INDEX file, too.

      Version 1.2 (12.02.97)
        - Index View and Integrate "understand" an INDEX file with an "age"
          column.
        - Getting the position and size of progress window is much more
          system friendly now.

      Version 1.21 (5.04.97)
        - Index View didn't work when Directory Opus was run. Fixed.

      Version 1.22 (12.10.97)
        - Index View should work in multitasking with every other program.
          The bug with bad accessing dos.library finally fixed (I hope).

      Version 1.23 (27.02.98)
        - Version string implemented.
        - Small bugfixes.

      Version 1.25 (11.06.98)
        - Index View 1.23 didn't display last two/three lines from the file
          list in the selected directory. Fixed.
        - No more memory loss. Earlier versions didn't free one of the
          buffers.
        - All programs from the package should behave better under low
          memory conditions.
        - Index View and Integrate should be significantly faster now.
        - Integrate and Fix Index delete INDEX.scan, because it's unusable
          after modification of the INDEX file anyway.
        - Format of an INDEX.scan file is changed. INDEX.scan prepared by
          previous versions of Index View must be deleted before running 1.25.
        - Small bug in Integrate fixed.
@endnode

